OL,3,CPlaid Cymru candidate steps down after
OL,4,Coffensive social media post uncovered
OL,6,FA Plaid Cymru candidate for May's
OL,7,FSenedd election has stepped down after
OL,8,Fan offensive tweet was uncovered.
OL,10,FNeil Roberts was placed fourth on the
OL,11,Fparty's list to contest Caerdydd
OL,12,FPenarth in May's election.
OL,14,FThe messages - which ITV News has
OL,15,Fchosen not to publish in full - were
OL,16,Fpart of an exchange on the social
OL,17,Fmedia platform Twitter (now X) in 2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
