OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774627872
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru candidate steps down after
OL,4,Coffensive social media post uncovered
OL,6,FMr Roberts was replying to a tweet
OL,7,Fwhich read: "Very against having kids
OL,8,Fjust for the sake of it. Don't have
OL,9,Fchildren if you're not capable of
OL,10,Fraising them."
OL,12,FHe responded by using a grossly
OL,13,Foffensive term about children,
OL,14,Ffollowed by "are for life not just for
OL,15,FChristmas"
OL,17,FNeil Roberts announced his withdrawal
OL,18,Fin a statement issued by Plaid Cymru
OL,19,Fshortly after midday on Thursday.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@JO]
