OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774627872
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru candidate steps down after
OL,4,Coffensive social media post uncovered
OL,6,F"Years ago, I made a comment using
OL,7,Fonline slang that was inappropriate
OL,8,Fand crude. The language I used was
OL,9,Fwrong, and I take full responsibility
OL,10,Ffor it. I apologise unreservedly for
OL,11,Fthe offence and concern it has caused.
OL,13,F"I recognise that those seeking public
OL,14,Foffice have a responsibility to
OL,15,Fpromote respectful and constructive
OL,16,Fdebate. This is something I have
OL,17,Fsought to do since entering politics,
OL,18,Fand will continue to strive towards.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
