PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774627872
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru candidate steps down after
OL,4,Coffensive social media post uncovered
OL,6,F"However, I do not want this to
OL,7,Fdetract from the campaign or from the
OL,8,Fissues that matter to our community. I
OL,9,Fam therefore stepping down as a
OL,10,Fcandidate with immediate effect."
OL,12,FAsked by ITV News if Mr Roberts
OL,13,Fremained a member of the party, a
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru spokesperson said "he is
OL,15,Fjust standing down as a candidate"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
